        "value": "Polymorph"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "I can draw upon the changeable nature of water to alter my own fundamental form.  I will first need to fill a Crystal Phylactery with the essence of a creature I want to become.  Then, I hold the spell in one hand and the phylactery in the other.  This will determine what shape I take on.\n\nThe magnitude of the effect may allow me to take on even more powerful forms.\n\n(Note: If Budschie's Morph Mod is not loaded, this component will not be available.)"
        }
      }
    ],
